'''''Other Minds''''' is an unofficial, non-profit magazine devoted to role-playing games set in [[J.R.R. Tolkien]]'s imaginary world. The magazine was initiated with the demise of ''[[Other Hands]]''.

''Other Minds'' is published in digital format and is edited by [[Thomas Morwinsky]] and [[Hawke Robinson]].
